[[File:Kevin_Rubio.jpg|thumb|250px|Kevin Rubio in ''Tag & Bink Are Dead'' 2]]
'''Kevin Rubio''' has written for ''Star Wars'' in a variety of media.

He wrote, directed, and provided a voice for the fan film ''TROOPS''. He was later hired by [[Dark Horse Comics|Dark Horse]] to pen several comics, including the [[Star Wars: Tag & Bink|''Tag and Bink'']] series and several stories for ''[[Star Wars Tales]]''. Rubio also wrote a number of humorous character interviews for ''[[Star Wars Insider]]''. On the television side, Rubio wrote an episode of ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' called "[[Bombad Jedi]]."

